cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection and tracking in videos. Additionally, the use of tracklets and conditioning the object detection on them suggests a machine learning (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.LG) approach. The proposed method also involves optimization and modeling of object trajectories, which could fall under robotics (cs.RO) or multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
